{
  "stem": "20088.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And it rained a lot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We had black Wellington boots.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And so I looked really like any other Dutch girl-- girls.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And we went out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We went shopping, and we went out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] it-- it wasn't really safe, because-- I didn't go to school, of course.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "That, I couldn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because if we would have been caught, this family would have gone to concentration camp as well.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And with their two little boys, you know, they didn't want to take that risk, which was understandable.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father and brother in the Hague were with another sister, and she as well after a while said it was too dangerous for her to keep.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It wasn't so organized yet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "People didn't have the backup of a lot of help from the organization.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was still too new.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we went to our contact, Mr.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Brooksma.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Or-- or we didn't go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He came.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, he visited regularly to see if he needed-- everything was rationed in Holland by that time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We had to have clothing coupons and food coupons.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It wasn't very much.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But we still got-- oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I just wanted to tell something else.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My father-- like I said, he provided for everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "When we were still not in hiding-- so from '40 till '42-- food started to become short supply.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he rented in the city a little room.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And there, there were suitcases.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we had to go and put food there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So we were only allowed, for instance, one packet of rice, and one tin of sardine, always in one shop.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But so we went a few times, and everybody went.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And so we got a lot of food together.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he puts it in this little room.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
